1
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:45,660
I found him.

2
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:48,440
The demon has just escaped the seal.

3
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:49,720
He is indeed very weak.

4
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,320
The sect reward this time

5
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:53,720
will definitely be mine.

6
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:54,480
Attack.

7
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:37,400
These disciples have demonic energy on them.

8
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,080
He should be nearby.

9
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Heal your wounds.

10
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,570
Where did you come from?

11
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,380
And how did you know I was here?

12
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,440
I came from a very faraway place.

13
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:15,100
What do you mean, where did I pop out from?

14
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,260
You'd better heal your wounds first.

15
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:23,040
You used to

16
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:25,700
hate providing blood for me, didn't you?

17
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,250
Why are you willing now?

18
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,400
I didn't know back then.

19
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,140
Any normal person would be scared

20
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,640
seeing their blood being sucked, alright?

21
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,120
But

22
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,600
it's different now.

23
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,800
You are a very important friend to me.

24
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,400
Of course,

25
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:44,280
I also hope you recover quickly.

26
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:46,560
Friend?

27
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,640
You, a human,

28
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:51,370
want to be friends with a demon like me?

29
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,610
What human or demon?

30
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,079
We are all living beings.

31
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:56,079
I treat everyone equally, alright?

32
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,720
The night I escaped the seal,

33
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,320
how did you know I was there?

34
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,640
How would I know?

35
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,540
It was just a coincidence.

36
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,890
If you don't want to tell me,

37
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,040
forget it.

38
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,280
Lanqi Moyuan,

39
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,200
wait for me!

40
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:22,960
Yiyi,

41
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,520
where did he go this time?

42
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:27,100
Judging by the direction,

43
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,460
it should be the Netherworld.

44
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,440
He's going back to the Demon Realm.

45
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,840
When he escaped the seal,

46
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:36,260
he didn't break it,

47
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,160
but transferred it to himself.

48
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:42,640
The seal will continuously consume his demonic energy.

49
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,440
Once it's depleted to the limit,

50
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,680
it will start consuming his life force.

51
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,520
When the seal spreads all over his body,

52
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,320
his life

53
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,730
will also come to an end.

54
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:54,360
So his return to the Netherworld to heal

55
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,400
is inevitable.

56
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,400
For me,

57
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,840
he was injured so badly that the seal appeared,

58
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,360
yet he said nothing.

59
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,680
Yiyi,

60
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:15,840
why do you think someone like him

61
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,769
would choose to destroy the world?

62
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,959
I can't understand his actions,

63
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,520
but I know the consequences of them.

64
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,160
Why is Lanqi so far away?

65
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,560
Why is the first spell I use

66
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,440
a floating spell for traveling?

67
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,360
If you don't hurry up and cultivate

68
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,600
to restore your spiritual power,

69
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,730
you'll feel the pain of its depletion.

70
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:23,040
Is there any justice left?

71
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:25,560
To maintain this so-called spiritual power,

72
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,560
all I do is cultivate every day.

73
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:30,220
I even have to cultivate while sleeping.

74
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,480
Is cultivating immortality this hard?

75
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:33,720
Hard?

76
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,320
TV shows are all lies.

77
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,280
Those

78
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,640
immortals

79
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,800
can easily move mountains

80
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,360
and destroy the world.

81
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,480
Where does all that spiritual power come from?

82
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,200
If they just gave me a tiny bit,

83
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,880
I'd already be in Lanqi.

84
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,640
It hurts!

85
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,360
Finally here.

86
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,840
Damn Lanqi Moyuan.

87
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,100
Even if you are the Demon King,

88
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,600
I can't take it anymore.

89
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,960
I'm definitely going to lose my temper.

90
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,040
So this is the Netherworld.

91
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:38,960
It's so dark

92
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,600
and depressing.

93
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,640
No wonder

94
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,400
staying in a place like this for too long

95
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:47,120
would give someone depression.

96
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,850
Depression?

97
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,770
What is that?

98
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,760
In your words,

99
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,640
it's

100
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,240
a heart disease

101
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,240
or an inner demon.

102
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,850
The Netherworld is where demons are born.

103
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,480
Demons

104
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,380
do not generate inner demons.

105
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,450
Alright.

106
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,760
Typical AI thinking.

107
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,330
I was just thinking,

108
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,720
Yuan is a half-blood after all.

109
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,240
He's half human.

110
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,360
So,

111
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,450
I think he probably wouldn't like this place.

112
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:13,840
He is right ahead.

113
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,400
If you want to find him,

114
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,330
I won't stop you.

115
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,120
But this is the Netherworld,

116
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,120
not a place for humans to set foot in.

117
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,530
Especially for you,

118
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,440
it's extremely dangerous here.

119
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,360
Have you ever thought about

120
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,960
what happens if you never find the reason why he destroyed the world,

121
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,690
or if you can't untie this knot?

122
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,440
He will eventually sacrifice you

123
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,840
or the Daughter of the World

124
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,370
and then destroy the world.

125
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:35,680
Yiyi.

126
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:36,920
If

127
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,500
this is the final outcome,

128
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,560
if

129
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:40,600
this world

130
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,800
is destined to be destroyed anyway,

131
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:44,280
then our deal has failed.

132
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,640
I'll die whether I go back or not,

133
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,890
so I might as well take a gamble.

134
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:50,650
Lu Danyu,

135
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,620
you'll be in great danger.

136
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:54,360
It's okay.

137
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,040
Yuan.

138
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:08,010
Why are you here?

139
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,880
Do you know where this is?

140
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,100
How dare a human

141
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,400
come here.

142
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,480
I just came to find you.

143
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:15,820
If you can come,

144
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,040
why can't I?

145
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:18,800
You...

146
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,760
Can you please not be mad?

147
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,280
Yuan.

148
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,540
Listen to me first.

149
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,120
I came here for a reason.

150
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,080
I want to know.

151
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,600
Hurry up.
